Usage: specifyJtag [-help] [-cell <cellName>] [-group <cellName|hinstName>]
                   [-groupWArea <cellName|hinstName> {width height}]
                   [-hinst <hinstName>] [-inst <instName>]
                   [-instGroup <instGroupName>]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cellName>               # cell name (wild card) to be made jtag cells
                               # (string, optional)
-group <cellName|hinstName>    # cell or hinst name to be made a jtag group
                               # cell (string, optional)
-groupWArea <cellName|hinstName> {width height}
                               # cell or hinst name to be made a jtag group
                               # cell with bounding box width and height
                               # (string, optional)
-hinst <hinstName>             # hinst name to be made jtag cell
                               # (string, optional)
-inst <instName>               # inst name (wild card) to be made jtag cell
                               # (string, optional)
-instGroup <instGroupName>     # instGroup name to be made jtag cell
                               # (string, optional)